    <name>Translit</name>
    <summary>Translit is a simple method of encoding Cyrillic letters with Latin ones like 'Vsem privet' 'Всем привет'</summary>
    <description>
        <p>Supported languages:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Russian</li>
            <li>Belarusian</li>
            <li>Ukrainian</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
